/**************************************************************************************
 * ------------------- Template Class --------------------
 *
 * 1. It's little bit different from the template function.
 * 2. In class template, compiler can't deduce the parametertype, we have to tell the compiler which data type we will using.
 * 
 * Syntax:
 *      template<class/typename T>
 *      class class_name
 *      {
 *          //body;
 *      };
 * 
***************************************************************************************/
/**************************************************************************************
 * ------------------- Template Class & function Outside the class--------------------
 *
 *  1. When we defining function, constructor outside the class, we have to again write that template statement above the defination
 *  
***************************************************************************************/

